maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.orig: There is no turning back now. Let's move forward, Lea!
maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.text: Пути назад нет. Давай двигаться вперёд, Лея!

maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.orig: So, did I get that right?
maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.text: Итак, я правильно понял?

maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.orig: My...\. "clone" is still over there in Evotarground?
maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.text: Мой...\. "клон" до сих пор там, в зоне эвотаров?

maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.orig: [nods]
maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.text: [кивает]

maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.orig: Oh Junge, this is such a weird situation.
maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.text: Oh Junge (Боже), это такая странная ситуация.

maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.orig: We both just barely know each other, right?
maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.text: Мы ведь едва знакомы друг с другом.

maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.orig: Yet that "other Lukas" seems to be quite dear to you, because of what you both experienced together.
maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.text: Но кажется, этот "другой Лукас" тебе очень дорог, из-за того, что вы оба пережили вместе.

maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.orig: [nods]
maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.text: [кивает]

maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.orig: It really shows how much your life is shaped by happenstance.
maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.text: Это в самом деле показывает, насколько наша жизнь определяется случайностью.

maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.orig: Also...\. I really wonder what would happen if I met my clone over there.
maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.text: Помимо этого...\. Мне действительно интересно, что произойдёт, если я встречу своего клона там.

maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.orig: [shakes head]
maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.text: [мотает головой]

maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.orig: Oh...\. I suppose I better be careful about that.
maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.text: Ох...\. Я полагаю, что мне лучше быть осторожным с этим.

maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.orig: [nods]
maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.text: [кивает]

maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.orig: Hi, Lea!
maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.text: Привет, Лея!

maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.orig: Hi?
maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.text: Привет?

maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.orig: Man, it's still so hard to believe that you are an AI.
maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.text: Мда, всё ещё трудно поверить, что ты искусственный интеллект.

maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.orig: Wait...\. does that mean you understand binary?
maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.text: Подожди...\. Значит ли это, что ты понимаешь двоичный код?

maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.orig: [shakes head]
maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.text: [мотает головой]

maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.orig: I have no idea what it means!\. You tell me!
maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.text: Я понятия не имею, что это значит!\. Ты мне скажи!

maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.orig: Nyahahahahahaha!
maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.text: Ньяхахахахахаха!

maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.orig: Really though, this is all very exciting!
maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.text: Хотя на самом деле, это всё очень интересно!

maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.orig: You have my vote for best newbie of the year!
maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.text: У тебя мой голос за лучшего новичка года!

maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.orig: Lea!
maps/forest/caves/exit-cave-01.json/enti.text: Лея!
